   666                              <1> setHandleCount:    ;ah = 67h
   667                              <1> ;Input: bx = Size of new file handle table for process
   668                              <1> ;Output: CF=NC -> Ok to make more handles
   669                              <1> ;        CF=CY -> ax = Error code
   670                              <1> ;Five cases to consider:
   671                              <1> ;       1) Allocating a new block of memory, copying PSP JFT to it, inc hdl cnt
   672                              <1> ;       2) Freeing a block and returning to the PSP JFT, dec hdl cnt x
   673                              <1> ;       3) Extending an external block, inc hdl cnt. If realloc fails, goto 5)
   674                              <1> ;       4) Reducing an external block, dec hdl cnt, no realloc.
   675                              <1> ;   Special case below, cannot be enacted directly by caller.
   676                              <1> ;       5) Freeing an external block for a bigger external block, inc hdl cnt
