   691 00003DC4 E96E3F0000          <1>     jmp extErrExit
   692                              <1> .reduceExternal:
   693                              <1> ;We try to reallocate the block to be more appropriate for the new maxhdls.
   694                              <1> ;If it fails, no big deal since we manually prevent the user from using more
   695                              <1> ; files. If we then grow this block again, realloc will try to grow it again
   696                              <1> ; and failing that, it will free it and then allocate a new block.
