  1827                              <1> buildSFTEntry:
  1828                              <1> ;Called in a critical section.
  1829                              <1> ;Input: ax = Any additional open mode bits to add
  1830                              <1> ;       STACK: File attributes if creating a file
  1831                              <1> ;       [currentSFT] = SFT we are building
  1832                              <1> ;   Has the following setup:
  1833                              <1> ;           .wOpenMode: Set with ok defaults
  1834                              <1> ;           .qPID: Set to PID for call
  1835                              <1> ;           .dMID: Set to MID for call
