    10                              <1> ;al = 03h => Write to Char device                     x
    11                              <1> ;al = 04h => Read from Block device                   x
    12                              <1> ;al = 05h => Write to Block device                    x
    13                              <1> ;======================================================
    14                              <1> ;IO Status Functions (optionally implemented)         |
    15                              <1> ;al = 06h => Get input status                         x
