    17                              <1> ;======================================================
    18                              <1> ;Device information (optionally implemented)          |  
    19                              <1> ;al = 08h => Is a block device removable?       
    20                              <1> ;al = 09h => Is a logical device local or remote?   
    21                              <1> ;al = 0Ah => Is a handle to a local or remote file?
