   854                              <1> getsetDiskSerial:  ;ah = 69h, get/set disk serial number
   855                              <1> ;Wraps the generic disk IO call to get/set the disk serial number and
   856                              <1> ; associated information.
   857                              <1> ;Input:
   858                              <1> ;   al = 0: Get disk serial number
